export default async(e,t={})=>{const c=document.createElement("a");c.download=t.fileName||"Untitled",c.href=URL.createObjectURL(e),c.addEventListener("click",(()=>{setTimeout((()=>URL.revokeObjectURL(c.href)),3e4)})),c.click()};
